title: Oceanic Gaming Community Tournament

embed.description: Battlefy is the simplest way to start, manage, and find esports tournaments | Create. Compete. Conquer.

body:
Interested in playing with your friends or just seeing how you compare against some other up and coming teams.

Then be sure to join our community tournament. Be sure to register to get some sweet RP rewards.
Finals match will be streamed.

We hold tournaments every Sunday from 2pm NZDT or 12pm AEDT. Hope to see you there.
